      <title>UNICREDIT将意大利人寿保险业带入国内</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-brings-italian-life-insurance-business-house-2025-06-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利的第二大银行UniCredit表示，它已将其意大利人寿保险业带入了众议院，并将申请为拥有保险公司的银行，称为“丹麦妥协”的资本救济措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-brings-italian-life-insurance-business-house-2025-06-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Jun 2025 17:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团雇用Drago Rajkovic担任JPMorgan并购的共和国，备忘录说</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-hires-drago-rajkovic-co-head-ma-jpmorgan-memo-says-2025-06-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据路透社在周五看到的备忘录，花旗集团（Citigroup）聘请了德拉戈·拉杰科维奇（Drago Rajkovic）作为竞争对手摩根大通（JPMorgan Chase）的合并和收购的共同收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-hires-drago-rajkovic-co-head-ma-jpmorgan-memo-says-2025-06-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Jun 2025 15:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
